{"type": "article", "id": 29772, "title": "羊毛猫咪床", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-18T22:47:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160718201713hdBfC4ocZkNzVjXA.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>如果你刚巧在为喵星人寻找一张能够巧妙地融合进室内环境的小床，elevele 出品的一系列羊毛猫咪床或许是一个不错的选择。这些形状各异的家具在喵星人不使用的时候同样可以当作收纳篮摆在房间里，用来放杂志或者是充电器、钱包等小物都绰绰有余。elevele 希望用这些漂亮的羊毛制品让人们意识到猫咪床不一定会给人带来突兀的感觉，它们也能成为小巧的家饰。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/elevele?section_id=13268353\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 87.44 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718202233h0rEaWUvwY8u5mV3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.428750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718202233VwQlvJq439Hc51Cu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.565000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}